hadiths[100]{hadithnumber,text}:
5251,"unhon-ne apni biwi (Aamna-binte-ghifaar) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane main (haalate-haiz mein) talaaq de di. Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq puchha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho ke apni biwi se rujoo kar lein aur phir apne nikah mein baqi rakhein. jab maahwaarii (haiz) band ho jaey, phir maahwaarii aaey aur phir band ho, tab agar chaahein to apni biwi ko apne nikah mein baqi rakhein aur agar chaahein to talaaq de dein (lekin talaaq us tuhur mein) unke sath ham-bistarii se pahley hona chahiye yahi (tuhur ki) wo muddat hai jis mein Allah Taala ne aurton ko talaaq dene ka hukm diya hai."
5252,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko haalate-haiz mein talaaq de di. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke chahiye ke rujoo kar lein. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya ye talaaq , talaaq samjhii jaeygi ? unhon-ne kaha ke chup reh. phir kya samjhii jaeygi ? aur Qatada ne bayan kya, unse Yunus bin Juber ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se) farmaya ke usey hukm do ke rujoo kar ley ( Yunus bin Juber ne bayan kya ke) maine poochha, kya ye talaaq talaaq samjhii jaeygi ? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha to kya samajhta hai agar koi kisi farz ke ada karne se aajiz bin jaey ya ahmaq ho jaey. to wo farz uske zimme se saaqit ho jaaeyga? hargiz nahi."
5253,ye talaaq jo maine haiz mein di thi mujh par shumaar ki gaee.
5254,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kin biwi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se panah mangi thi? unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unhein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ke Joon ki beti (Umaima ya Asma ( jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan ( nikah ke baad) laai gain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas gaey to usne ye keh diya ke main tum se Allah ki panah maangtii hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tum ne bahut badi cheez se panah mangi hai, apne Maikey chali jao. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne is hadis ko Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf bin abi Muneea' se, usne bhi apne dada Abu-Munee'a ( Ubaidullah bin abi-Ziyad ( se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai."
5255,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bahar nikley aur aik baagh mein pahunchey jiska naam ''Shaut'' tha. jab wahan ja kar aur baaghon ke darmyan pahunchey to baith gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log yahin baitho , phir baagh mein gaey, jauniya laai ja chuki thin aur unhein khajoor ke aik ghar mein utaaraa. uska naam Umaima binte- Nauman bin Sharaheel tha. unke sath aik daaya bhi unki dekh bhaal ke liye thi. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas gaey to farmaya ke apne aapko mere hawale kar de. usne kaha kya koi shahzaadii kisi aam aadmi ke liye apne aapko hawale kar sakti hai? bayan kya ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna shafqat ka hath unki taraf badha kar uske sar par rakha to usne kaha ke main tum se Allah ki panah maangtii hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne usi se panah mangi jis se panah mangi jati hai. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke abu-Usaid ! usey 2 raazqiya kapdey pehna kar usey uske ghar pahuncha aao."
5256,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umaima-bint-Sharaaheel se nikah kya tha, phir jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan laai gaiin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf hath badhaya jisey usne na-pasand kya. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke unka saman kar dein aur Raazqiya ke 2 kapdey unhein pahnney ke liye de dein."
5257,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umaima binte- Sharaheel se nikah kya tha, phir jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan laai gain . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf hath badhaya jisey usne na-pasand kya. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke unka saman kar dein aur Raazqiya ke 2 kapdey unhein pahnney ke liye de dein."
5258,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya : aik shakhs ne apni biwi ko us waqt talaaq di jab wo haaiza thi ( iska kya hukm ? ( is par unhon-ne kaha tum ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jantey ho? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko us waqt talaaq di thi jab wo haaiza thin. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, iske mutaalliq aap se poochha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke) ibne-Umar us waqt apni biwi se) raj'at (apni bevi ki taaf palat jaayein) kar lein, phir jab wo haiz se paak ho jayen to us waqt agar ibne-Umar chaahein, unhein talaaq dein. maine arz kya : kya usey bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talaaq shumaar kya tha? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar koi aajiz hai aur himaaqat ka saboot de to uska ilaaj hai."
5259,"Uwemir Ajlani (Raziallahu anhu) Aasim bin Adi Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse kaha ke aey Aasim! tumhara kya khayal hai, agar koi apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair ko dekhey to kya usey wo qatl kar sakta hai? lekin phir tum qisaas mein usey ( shauhar ko) bhi qatl kar doge ya phir wo kya karega? Aasim mere liye ye masla aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochh dijiye. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye masla puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un sawalat ko na-pasand farmaya aur is silsiley main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kalimaat Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) par nagawar guzrey aur jab wo wapas apne ghar aagey to Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne aa kar unse puchha ke bataiye aap se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaayaa? Aasim ne is par kaha tum ne mujh ko aafat mein dala. jo sawal tum ne puchha tha wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na-gawar guzra . Uwemir ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! ye masla Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochhey baghair mein baaz nahi aaoonga . chunanche wo rawaana huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke darmyan mein tashrif rakhtey they. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! agar koi shakhs apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair ko pa leta hai to aap ka kya khayal hai? kya wo usey qatl kar de ? lekin is sura mein aap usey qatl kar dengey ya phir usey kya karna chahiye ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumhari biwi ke barey mein wahi nazil ki hai, isliye tum jao aur apni biwi ko bhi sath laao. Sehal ne bayan kya ke phir donon ( miyan biwi ( ne liaan kya. logon ke sath mein bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us waqt maujood tha. liaan se jab donon farigh huey to Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! agar iske baad bhi mein usey apne paas rakhoon to ( iska matlab ye hoga ke) mein jhoota hun. chunanche unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se pahley hi apni biwi ko teen talaaq di. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke phir liaan karne waley ke liye yahi tariqa jari ho gaya."
5260,"mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unhein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Rifaa qarzii (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Rifaa ne mujhey talaaq de di thi aur talaaq bhi baain, phir maine iske baad Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber qarzii (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kar liya lekin unke paas to kapdey ke pallu jaisa hai (yani wo naa-mard hain). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaaliban tum Rifaa ke paas dobara jana chahti ho lekin aisa us waqt tak nahi ho sakta jab tak tum apne maujooda shauhar ka mazaa na chakh lo aur wo tumhara maza na chakh ley."
5261,"aik sahib ne apni biwi ko teen talaaq de di thi. unki biwi ne dusri shadi kar li, phir doosrey shauhar ne bhi) ham-bistarii se pahley) unhein talaaq de di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya gaya ke kya pahlaa shauhar ab unke liye halal hai (ke unse dobara shadi kar lein). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, yahan tak ke wo yani shauhar saanii uska maza chakhey jaisa ke pahley ne maza chakhaa tha."
5262,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ikhtiyar diya tha aur ham ne Allah aur uske rasool ko hi pasand kya tha lekin iska hamarey haq mein koi shumaar ( talaaq ( mein nahi hua tha.
5263,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se '' ikhtiyar '' ke mutaalliq sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ikhtiyar diya tha to kya mahz ye ikhtiyar talaaq bin jata. Masruq ne kaha ke ikhtiyar dene ke baad agar tum mujhey pasand kar leti ho to uski koi haisiyat nahi, chahey mein aik martaba ikhtiyar dun ya so martaba ( talaaq nahi hogi) ."
5264,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se agar aisey shakhs ka masla puchha jata jisne apni biwi ko teen talaaq di hoti, to wo kehtey agar to aik baar ya 2 baar talaaq deta to rujoo kar sakta tha kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko aisa hi hukm diya tha lekin jab tu ney teen talaaq de di to wo aurat ab tujh par haram ho gaee yahan tak ke wo terey siwa aur kisi shakhs se nikah kare."
5265,"aik shakhs Rifaaii ne apni biwi ( tameema binte- Wahab ( ko talaaq de di, phir aik doosrey shakhs se unki biwi ne nikah kya lekin unhon-ne bhi unko talaaq de di. un doosrey shauhar ke paas kapdey ke pallu ki tarah tha. aurat ko us se pura maza jaisa wo chahti thi nahi mila. aakhir Abdur-Rehman ne thodey hi dinon rakh kar usko talaaq de di. ab wo aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! mere shauhar ne mujhey talaaq de di thi, phir maine aik doosrey mard se nikah kya. wo mere paas tanhai mein aaey lekin unke sath to kapdey ke pallu ki tarah ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. kal aik hi baar us ne mujh se sohbat ki wo bhi bekaar (dukhool hi nahi hua uper hi uper chhu kar reh gaya) kya ab main apne pahley khawind ke liye halal ho gaee ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to apne pahley khawind ke liye halal nahi ho sakti jab tak doosra khawind teri sheernii na chakhey."
5266,agar kisi ne apni biwi ko apne uper haram kaha to ye koi cheez nahi aur farmaya ke tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki pairwi umda pairwi hai.
5267,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ummul-Momenin Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan thahartey they aur unke yahan shehad piyaa kartey they. chunanche maine aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne mil kar salaah ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham mein se jiske yahan bhi tashrif laaein to aap se ye kaha jaey ke aap ke munh se maghaafeer (eik khas qism ke badbudar gond) ki mahak aati hai, kya aap ne maghaafeer khaya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske baad ham mein se aik ke yahan tashrif laey to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi baat kahi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke maine Zenab binte-Jahash ke yahan shehad piyaa hai, ab dobara nahi piyunga. is par ye aayat nazil huii ( ya أيها النبي لم تحرم ما أحل الله لك‏ ) ke ''aey Nabi ! aap wo cheez kyon haram kartey hain jo Allah ne aap ke liye halal ki hai.'' se ( ‏‏‏‏إن تتوبا إلى الله‏ ( tak. ye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf Khattab hai (وإذ أسر النبي إلى بعض أزواجه) . hadis se aap ka yahi farmana murad hai ke maine maghaafeer nahi khaya balke shehad piyaa hai."
5268,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shehad aur meethii cheezein pasand kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz se farigh ho kar jab wapas aatey to apni beeviyon ke paas wapas tashrif ley jatey aur kuchh se qareeb bhi hotey they. aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hafsa-binte-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif le gaey aur mamool (routine) se zyada der unke ghar thahrey. mujhey is par ghairat aai aur maine iske barey mein puchha to malum hua ke Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko unki qaum ki kisi khatun ne unhein shehad ka aik dabba diya hai aur unhon-ne usi ka sharbat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pesh kya hai. maine apne ji mein kaha : Allah ki qism ! main to aik heela karoongii, phir maine Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumharey paas aaeingey aur jab aaein to kehna ke malum hota hai aap ne maghaafeer kha rakha hai? zahir hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske jawab mein inkar karengey. us waqt kehna ke phir ye boo kaisi hai jo aap ke munh se malum kar rahi hoon? is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahengey ke Hafsa ne shehad ka sharbat mujhey pilaya hai. tum kehna ke ghaaliban us shehad ki makkhii ne maghaafeer ke darakht ka arq choosaa hoga. mein bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi kahoongii aur Safiya tum bhi yahi kehna . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Sauda (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin ke Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) junhii darwazey par aa kar khadey huey to tumharey khof se maine irada kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wo baat kahun jo tum ne mujh se kahi thi. chunanche jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ke qareeb tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ne maghaafeer khaya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. unhon-ne kaha, phir ye bo kaisi hai jo aap ke munh se mehsus karti hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Hafsa ne mujhey shehad ka sharbat pilaya hai. is par Sauda (Raziallahu anha) boliin us shehad ki makkhii ne maghaafeer ke darakht ka arq choosaa hoga. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey to maine bhi yahi baat kahi iske baad jab Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne bhi usi ko dohraya . iske baad jab phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! wo shehad phir nosh farmaaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey uski zarurat nahi hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke is par Sauda boliin, Allah ki qism ! ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rokney mein kaamyaab ho gaey, maine unse kaha ke abhi chup raho."
5269,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne meri ummat ko burey khayalat ki had tak maaf kya hai, jab tak ke is par amal na karey ya usey zaban se ada na kare. Qatada (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke agar kisi ne apne dil mein talaaq de di to uska eitibaar nahi hoga jab tak zaban se na kahey ."
5270,"qabila Aslam ke aik sahib Maaiz naam ke masjid main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke unhon-ne zina kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse munh mod liya lekin phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aagey (aur zina ka iqrar kya ( phir unhon-ne apne uper char martaba shahadat di to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mukhaatab kartey huey farmaya ke tum paagal to nahi ho, kya waqei tum ne zina kya hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan , phir aap ne puchha kya to shadi shuda hai? usne kaha ke ji haan ho chuki hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein eidgaah par rajm (sangsaar) karne ka hukm diya. jab unhein patthar laga to wo bhaagney lagey lekin unhein Harra ke paas pakda aur jaan se mar diya gaya."
5271,"qabila Aslam ka aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif rakhtey they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mukhaatab kya aur arz kya ke unhon-ne zina kar liya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse munh mod liya hai lekin wo aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us rukh ki taraf mud gaya, jidhar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehra Mubarak pher liya tha aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! doosrey (yani khud ( ne zina kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi munh mod liya lekin wo phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us rukh ki taraf aa gaya jidhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne munh mod liya tha aur yahi arz kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir unse munh mod liya, phir jab chothi martaba wo isi tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aa gaya aur apne uper us ne char martaba (zinaa ki) shahadat di to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tum paagal to nahi ho? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke unhein ley jao aur sangsaar karo kyonke wo shadi shuda they."
5272,mujhey aik aisey shakhs ne khabar di jinhoney Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha ke unhon-ne bayan kya ke main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney un sahabi ko sangsaar kya tha. ham ne Madina Munawra ki eidgaah par sangsaar kya tha. jab un par patthar padaa to wo bhaagney lagey lekin ham ne unhein Harra mein phir pakad liya aur unhein sangsaar kya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey.
5273,Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey unke akhlaq aur Deen ki wjah se unse koi shikayat nahi hai. albatta mein Islam mein kufr ko pasand nahi karti . (kyonke unke sath reh kar unke huquq zaujiyat ko nahi ada kar sakti ( . is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke kya tum unka baagh (jo unhon-ne mehar mein diya tha) wapas kar sakti ho? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se) farmaya ke baagh qabool kar lo aur unhein talaaq de do.
5274,"aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya tha ke kya tum un ( Sabit (Raziallahu anhu)) ka baagh wapas kar dogii? unhon-ne arz kya haan kar doongii. chunanche unhon-ne baagh wapas kar diya aur unhon-ne unke shauhar ko hukm diya ke unhein talaaq de dein. aur Ibrahim bin tahmaan ne bayan kya ke unse Khalid ne, unse Ikrima ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur (is riwayat mein bayan kya ke) unke shauhar ( Sabit (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein talaaq de di."
5275,Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mujhey Sabit ke Deen aur unke akhlaq ki wjah se koi shikayat nahi hai lekin main unke sath guzaara nahi kar sakti . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir kya tum unka baagh wapas kar sakti ho? unhon-ne arz kya ji haan.
5276,Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaiin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Sabit ke Deen aur unke akhlaq se mujhey koi shikayat nahi lekin mujhey khatrah hai (ke mein Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki na-shukri mein na phans jaaun). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par unse malum farmaya ke kya tum unka baagh (jo unhon-ne mehar mein diya tha) wapas kar sakti ho? unhon-ne arz kya ji haan. chunanche unhon-ne wo baagh wapas kar diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein apne se juda kar diya.
5277,unse Ikrima ne yahi qissa (mursalan) naql kya aur is mein khatun ka naam jameela aaya hai.
5278,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke bani Mughira ne uski ijazat mangi hai ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se wo apni beti ka nikah kar lein lekin main unhein uski ijazat nahi doonga ."
5279,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) se Deen ke teen masley malum ho gaey. awwal ye ke unhein aazad kya gaya aur phir unke shauhar ke barey mein ikhtiyar diya gaya (ke chaahein unke nikah mein rahen warna alag ho jayen (aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unhein ke barey mein) farmaya ke 'walaa' usi se qaaim hoti hai jo aazad karey aur aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein tashrif laey to aik handi mein gosht pakaya ja raha tha, phir khaney ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney roti aur ghar ka saalan pesh kya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine to dekha ke handi mein gosht bhi paak raha hai? arz kya gaya ke ji haan lekin wo gosht Barira ko sadqe mein mila hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sadqa nahi khaatey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo unke liye sadqa hai aur hamarey liye Barira ki taraf se tohfa hai."
5280,maine unhein ghulam dekha tha. aap ki murad Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar se thi.
5281,ye Mughees bani falan ke ghulam they. aap ka ishara Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar ki taraf tha. maano us waqt bhi main unhein dekh raha hun ke Madina ki galiyon mein wo Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey peechhey rotey phir rahe hain.
5282,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar aik habshi ghulam they. unka Mughees naam tha, wo bani falan ke ghulam they. jaisey wo manzar ab bhi meri aankhon mein hai ke wo Madina ki galiyon mein Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey peechhey phir rahe hain."
5283,Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar ghulam they aur unka naam Mughees tha. maano mein is waqt usko dekh raha hun jab wo Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey peechhey rotey huey phir rahe they aur aansuon se unki dadhi tar ho rahi thi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Abbas ! kya tumhen Mughees ki Barira se mohabbat aur Barira ki Mughees se nafrat par hairat nahi huii? aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke kash! ! tum iske barey mein apna faisla badal detiin. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap mujhey iska hukm farma rahe hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main sirf sifarish kar raha hun. unhon-ne is par kaha ke mujhey Mughees ke paas rehney ki khahish nahi hai.
5284,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko kharidney ka irada kya lekin unke maalikon ne kaha ke wo usi shart par unhein beech saktey hain ke Barira ka tarka ham lein aur unke sath 'walaa' ( aazadi ke baad) unhein se qaaim ho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jab iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya ke unhein khareed kar aazad kar do. tarka to usi ko milega jo londi ghulam ko aazad karey aur 'walaa' bhi usi ke sath qaaim ho sakti hai jo aazad karey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney gosht laya gaya phir kaha ke ye gosht Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko sadqa kya gaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo unke liye sadqa hai aur hamarey liye unka tohfa hai. ham se Aadam-bin-abii-Ayaas ne bayan kya, unse Shoba ne bayan kya aur is riwayat mein ye izafa kya ke phir (aazaadii ke baad) unhein unke shauhar ke mutaalliq ikhtiyar diya gaya (ke chaahein unke paas rahen aur agar chaahein unse apna nikah tod lein)."
5285,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se agar Yahudi ya nasara aurton se nikah ke mutaalliq sawal kya jata to wo kehtey ke Allah Taala ne mushrik aurton se nikah mominon ke liye haram qarar diya hai aur main nahi samajhta ke us se badh kar aur kya shirk hoga ke aik aurat ye kahey ke iske rab Esa (Alaihissalam) hain halanke wo Allah ke maqbool bandon mein se aik maqbool bandey hain.
5286,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur momineen ke liye mushrekeen 2 tarah ke they. aik to mushrekeen ladai karne walon se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse jang kartey they aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jang kartey they. doosrey ahad w paiman karne waley mushrekeen ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse jang nahi kartey they aur na wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jang kartey they aur jab ahle-kitab Harab ki koi aurat (Islam qabool karne ke baad) hijrat karke (Madina Munawra ( aati to unhein us waqt tak paigham nikah na diya jata yahan tak ke unhein haiz aata aur phir wo us se paak hotin, phir jab wo paak ho jaatiin to unse nikah jaaiz ho jata, phir agar unke shauhar bhi, unke kisi doosrey shakhs se nikah kar leney se pahley hijrat karke aa jatey to ye unhiin ko miltiin aur agar mushrekeen mein se koi ghulam ya londi musalman ho kar hijrat karti to wo aazad samjhey jatey aur unke wahi huquq hotey jo tamam muhajireen ke they. phir Ata ne muaahida mushrekeen ke silsiley mein Mujahid ki hadis ki tarah se soorate-haal bayan ki ke agar muaahida mushrekeen ki koi ghulam ya londi hijrat karke aa jati to unhein unke Malik mushrekeen ko wapas nahi kya jata tha. albatta jo unki qeemat hoti wo wapas kar di jati thi."
5287,"qareeba binte- abi Umayya umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( mushrekeen se nikah ki mukhalifat ki aayat ke baad) unhein talaaq de di to Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse nikah kar liya aur umme-hakam binte- abi Sufiyan ayaaz bin ghanam fahrii ke nikah mein thin, us waqt us ne unhein talaaq de di (aur wo Madina hijrat karke aa gaiin) aur Abdullah-bin-Usman Saqafi ne unse nikah kya."
5288,"mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke momin auratein jab hijrat karke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aati thin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein aazmaaney they b-wajah Allah Taala ke us irshad ke) ya أيها الذين آمنوا إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن‏ (ke ''aey wo logo ! jo eman ley aaey ho, jab momin auratein tumharey paas hijrat karke aaein to unhein aazmao '' . aakhir aayat tak. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir un ( hijrat karne wali) momin aurton mein se jo us shart ka iqrar kar leti (jiska zikr isi sura al-Mumtahina mein hai ke ''Allah ka kisi ko Sharik na thahraaogii'') to wo aazmaish mein poori samjhii jati thi. chunanche jab wo iska apni zaban se iqrar kar letin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse farmatey ke ab jao maine tum se ahad ley liya hai. hargiz nahin! Allah ki qasam! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ne (bait letey waqt) kisi aurat ka hath kabhi nahi chhuwaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse sirf zaban se (bait letey they). Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton se sirf unhein chizon ka ahad liya jinka Allah ne aapko hukm diya tha. bait leney ke baad aap unse farmatey ke maine tum se ahad ley liya hai. ye aap sirf zaban se kehtey ke maine tum se bait ley li."
5289,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni paak beeviyon se iilaa kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon mein moch aa gaee thi. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne bula khaane mein untees din tak qiyam farmaya, phir aap wahan se utrey. logon ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne aik mahina ka iilaa kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai."
5290,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us iilaa ke barey mein jiska zikr Allah Taala ne kya hai, farmatey they ke muddat poori honey ke baad kisi ke liye jaaiz nahi, siwa iske ke qaayde ke mutabiq (apni biwi ko) apne paas hi rok ley ya phir talaaq de, jaisa ke Allah Taala ne hukm diya hai. aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mujh se Ismail ne bayan kya ke unse Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke char mahiney guzar jayen to usey qazi ke samney pesh kya jaeyga yahan tak ke wo talaaq dedey aur talaaq us waqt tak nahi hoti jab tak talaaq di na jaey aur Usmaan, Ali, abu-Darda aur Aaisha aur baara doosrey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi aisa hi manqul hai."
5291,"jab char mahiney guzar jayen to usey qazi ke samney pesh kya jaeyga yahan tak ke wo talaaq dedey, aur talaaq us waqt tak nahi hoti jab tak talaaq di na jaey, aur Usmaan, Ali, abu-Darda aur Aaisha aur baara doosrey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi aisa hi manqul hai."
5292,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoii hui bakri ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pakad lo, kyonke ya wo tumhari hogi (agar aik saal tak elaan ke baad iska Malik na milaa). tumharey kisi bhai ki hogi ya phir bhediye ki hogi (agar unhi jangalon mein phirtii rahii) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoey huey oont ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya to aap ghussa ho gaey aur ghusse ki wjah se aap ke donon rukhsar surkh ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen us se kya gharaz! uske paas ( mazbut ( khur hain ( jiski wjah se chalney mein usey koi dushwari nahi hogi) uske paas mishkeeza hai jis se wo pani peetaa rahega aur darakht ke patey khata rahega , yahan tak ke iska Malik usey pa lega aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski rassii ka (jis se wo bandhaa ho (aur uske bartan ka (jis mein wo rakha ho) elaan karo aur uska aik saal tak elaan karo, phir agar koi aisa shakhs aa jaey jo usey pehchanta ho (aur iska Malik ho to usey de do) warna usey apne maal ke sath mila lo. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya ke phir main Rabee bin Abdur-Rehman se mila aur mujhey unse iske siwa aur koi cheez mehfooz nahi hai. maine unse puchha tha ke gum hui chizon ke barey mein manbais ke Maula Yazeed ki hadis ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? kya wo Zaid-bin-Khalid se manqul hai? to unhon-ne kaha ke haan, (Sufiyaan ne bayan kya ke yahan ( Yahya ne bayan kya ke Rabee ne manbais ke Maula Yazeed se bayan kya, unse Zaid-bin-Khalid ne. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke phir maine Rabee se mulaqat ki aur unse iske mutaalliq poochha."
5293,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf apne oont par Sawar ho kar kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi rukn ke paas aatey to uski taraf ishara karke takbeer kehtey aur Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yaajooj maajooj ke diwar mein itna suraakh ho gaya hai aur aap ne apni ungliyon se nawwey ka adad banaya.
5294,abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Juma mein aik ghadi aisi aati hai jo musalman bhi us waqt khada Namaz padhey aur Allah se koi khair maangey to Allah usey zaroor dega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is sa'at ki wazaahat kartey huey) apne hath se ishara kya aur apni ungliyon ko darmyani ungli aur chhoti ungli ke beech mein rakha jis se ham ne samjha ke aap us sa'at ko bahut mukhtasar honey ko bata rahe hain.
5295,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aik Yahudi ne aik ladki par zulm kya, iske chandi ke zewaraat jo wo pahney huey thi chheen liye aur iska sar kuchal diya. ladki ke ghar waley usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey to uski zindagi ki bas aakhiri ghadi baqi thi aur wo bol nahi sakti thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke tumhen kis ne maara hai? falan ne? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqia se ghair mutaalliq aadmi ka naam liya. isliye us ne apne sar ke ishaare se kaha ke nahi. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik doosrey shakhs ka naam liya aur wo bhi us waaqie se ghair mutaalliq tha to ladki ne sar ke ishara se kaha ke nahi, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke falan ne tumhen maara hai? to us ladki ne sar ke ishara se haan kaha,"
5296,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke fitna idhar se uthega aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashriq ki taraf ishara kya.
5297,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they. jab suraj doob gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahabi ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) se farmaya ke utar kar mere liye sattu ghol (kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they) unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! agar andhera honey dein to behtar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke utar kar sattu ghol . unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! agar aap aur andhera ho leney dein to behtar hai, abhi din baqi hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke utro aur sattu ghol lo. aakhir teesri martaba kehney par unhon-ne utar kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sattu gholaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa, phir aap ne apne hath se mashriq ki taraf ishara kya aur farmaya ke jab tum dekho ke raat idhar se aa rahi hai to roze-daar ko iftaar kar lena chahiye"
5298,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se kisi ko (sehrii khaney se) Bilal ki pukar na rokey ya aap ne farmaya ke ''unkii azaan'' kyonke wo pukaartey hain, ya farmaya, azan detey hain taake us waqt Namaz padhney wala ruk jaey. iska elaan se ye maqsud nahi hota ke subah sadiq ho gaee. us waqt Yazeed bin Zaree ne apne donon hath buland kiye (subah ki sura bataaney ke liye) phir aik hath ko doosrey par phailaayaa ( subah sadiq ki sura ke izhar ke liye) ."
5299,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kanjoos aur data ki misal 2 aadmiyon jaisi hai jin par lohey ki 2 zirahein seeney se gardan tak hain. data jab bhi koi cheez kharch karta hai to zirah iske chamdey par dheelii ho jati hai aur uske paon ki ungliyon tak pahunch jati hai (aur phail kar itni badh jati hai ke) iske nishaane-qadam ko mitaatii chaltii hai lekin kanjoos jab bhi kharch ka irada karta hai to uski zirah ka har halqa apni apni jagah chimat jata hai, wo usey dhila karna chahta hai lekin wo dhila nahi hota. us waqt aap ne apni ungli se apne halaq ki taraf ishara kya."
5300,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen bataaun ke qabila Ansar ka sabse behtar gharaana kon sa hai? sahaba ne arz kya ke zaroor bataiye ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banu-Najjaar kaa. iske baad unka martaba hai jo unse qareeb hain yani banu-abdul-ash'hal ka, unke baad wo hain jo unse qareeb hain, bani al-Haaris bin khazraj kaa. iske baad wo hain jo unse qareeb hain, banu-saaida kaa. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara kya aur apni muththii band ki, phir usey is tarah khola jaisey koi apne hath ki cheez ko phainktaa hai phir farmaya ke Ansar ke har gharaana mein khair hai."
5301,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri bea'sat qiyamat se itni qareeb hai jaisey uski us se (yani shahadat ki ungli beech ki ungli se) ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (raawii ko shak tha) ke jaisey ye donon ungliyan hain aur aap ne shahadat ki aur beech ki ungliyon ko mila kar bataya."
5302,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mahina itney , itney aur itney dinon ka hota hai. aap ki murad tees din se thi. phir farmaya aur itney , itney aur itney dinon ka bhi hota hai. aap ka ishara untees dinon ki taraf tha. aik martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tees ki taraf ishara kya aur dusri martaba untees ki taraf ."
5303,aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se Yaman ki taraf ishara karke farmaya ke barkatein idhar hain. 2 martaba (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ( haan aur dil ki sakhti unki kadak awaz walon mein hai jahan se shaitan ki donon seengein nikalti hain yani Rabee aur muzar mein.
5304,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aur yateem ki parwarish karne wala jannat mein is tarah hongey aur aap ne shahadat ki ungli aur beech ki ungli se ishara kya aur in donon ungliyon ke darmyan thodi si jagah khuli rakhii.
5305,aik sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere yahan to kala kalootaa bachcha paida hua hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey paas kuchh oont bhi hain? unhon-ne kaha ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke unke rang kaisey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke surkh rang ke hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke unmein koi siyaahii maail safaid oont bhi hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir ye kahan se aa gaya? unhon-ne kaha ke apni nasl ke kisi bahut pahley ke oont par ye padaa hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah tumhara ye ladka bhi apni nasl ke kisi door ke rishtedar par padaa hoga.
5306,qabila Ansar ke aik sahabi ne apni biwi par tohmat lagai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon miyan biwi se qism khilwaaii aur phir donon mein judai kara di.
5307,"Hilal bin Umayya ne apni biwi par tohmat lagaaii, phir wo aaey aur gawahi di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai ke tum mein se aik jhoota hai, to kya tum mein se koi (jo waqei gunah ka murtakib hua ho ( rujoo karega? iske baad unki biwi khadi huin aur unhon-ne gawahi di apne barii honey ki."
5308,"Aasim aap ka kya khayal hai ke aik shakhs agar apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekhey to kya usey qatl kar dega lekin phir aap log usey bhi qatl kar dengey. aakhir usey kya karna chaahiye? Aasim ! mere liye ye masla poochh do. chunanche Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye masla poochha. Nabi Karim ne is tarah ke sawalat ko na-pasand farmaya aur izhar na-gawari kya. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne is silsiley main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo kuchh suna uska bahut asar liya. phir jab ghar wapas aaey to Uwemir unke paas aaey aur poochha. Aasim ! aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya jawab diya. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Uwemir ! tum ne mere sath achchha mamla nahi kya, jo masla tum ne puchha tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey na-pasand farmaya, Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! jab tak mein ye masla Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum na kar loon , baaz nahi aaoonga . chunanche Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt sahaba ke darmyan mein maujood they. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ka us shakhs ke mutaalliq kya irshad hai jo apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekhey , kya usey qatl kar de ? lekin phir aap log usey ( qisaas ( mein qatl kar dengey , to phir usey kya karna chahiye ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey aur tumhari biwi ke barey mein abhi wahi nazil hui hai. jao aur apni biwi ko lekar aao . Sehal ne bayan kya ke phir un donon ne liaan kya. main bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas us waqt maujood tha. jab liaan se farigh huey to Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! agar ab bhi mein usey (apni biwi ko) apne sath rakhta hun to uska matlab ye hai ke main jhoota hun. chunanche unhon-ne unhein teen talaaqein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se pahley hi de dein. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke phir liaan karne walon ke liye sunnat tariqa muqarrar ho gaya."
5309,"mujhey ibne-Shahab ne liaan ke barey mein aur ye ke shariiat ki taraf se iska sunnat tariqa kya hai, khabar di bani saaida ke Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unhon-ne bayan kya ke qabila Ansar ke aik sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us shakhs ke mutaalliq aap ka kya irshad hai jo apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekhey , kya wo usey qatl kar de ya usey kya karna chahiye ? unhiin ke barey mein Allah Taala ne Quran Majeed ki wo aayat nazil ki jis mein liaan karne walon ke liye tafseelaat bayan hui hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumhari biwi ke barey mein faisla kar diya hai. bayan kya ke phir donon ne masjid mein liaan kya, main us waqt wahan maujood tha. jab donon liaan se farigh huey to Ansari sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! agar ab bhi mein usey apne nikah mein rakhoon to iska matlab ye hoga ke maine is par jhooti tohmat lagai thi. chunanche liaan se farigh honey ke baad unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se pahley hi unhein teen talaaqein de din. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein hi unhein juda kar diya. (Sahal ne ya ibne-Shahab ne) kaha ke har liaan karne waley miyaan-beewii ke darmyan yahi judai ka sunnat tariqa muqarrar hua. ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke unke baad shariiat ki taraf se tariqa ye mutaiyan hua ke 2 liaan karne walon ke darmyan tafreeq kara di jaya kare. aur wo aurat haamla thi aur unka betaa apni maa ki taraf mansub kya jata tha. bayan kya ke phir aisi aurat ke meeraas ke barey mein bhi ye tariqa shariiat ki taraf se muqarrar ho gaya ke bachcha iska waaris hoga aur wo bachche ki waaris hogi. iske mutabiq jo Allah Taala ne wiraasat ke silsile mein farz kya hai. ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Shahab ne aur unse Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne, usi hadis mein ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar (li'aan karne wali khaatoon) us ne surkh aur pasta qad bachcha janaa jaisey وحرہ to main samjhoonga ke aurat hi sachchii hai aur uske shauhar ne is par jhooti tohmat lagai hai lekin agar kaalaa, badi aankhon wala aur badey sirinon (pushton) wala bachcha janaa to main samjhoonga ke shauhar ne iske mutaalliq sach kaha tha. (aurat jhooti hai) jab bachcha paida ho to wo buri shakl ka tha (yani us mard ki sura par jis se wo badnaam hui thi)."
5310,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein liaan ka zikr hua aur Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne us silsile mein koi baat kahi (ke mein agar apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekh loon to wahin qatl kar doon) aur chaley gaey, phir unki qaum ke aik sahabi ( Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu)) unke paas aaey ye shikayat ley karke unhon-ne apni biwi ke sath aik ghair mard ko paya hai. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey aaj ye aazmaish meri usi baat ki wjah se aai (jo aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kahi thi). phir wo unhein lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo waqia bataya jis mein mulawwis us sahabi ne apni bevi ko paya tha. ye sahib zard rang, kam gosht waley (patley-dubley) aur seedhey baal waley they aur jiske mutaalliq unhon-ne dawa kya tha ke usey unhon-ne apni biwi ke sath ( tanhai mein) paya , wo gathey huey jism ka, gehunwey aur bharey gosht wala tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ke aey Allah ! is maamle ko saaf kar de. chunanche us aurat ne bachcha usi mard ki shakl ka janaa jiske mutaalliq shauhar ne dawa kya tha ke usey unhon-ne apni biwi ke sath paya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne miyaan-beewii ke darmyan liaan karaya. aik shagird ne majlis mein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya yahi wo aurat hai jiske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar main kisi ko bila gawahi ke sangsaar kar sakta to is aurat ko sangsaar karta. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi (ye jumla Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) us aurat ke mutaalliq farmaya tha jiski badkaarii Islam ke zamane mein khul gaee thi. Abu-Saleh aur Abdullah-bin Yusuf ne is hadis mein bajaey ( خدلا‏ . Mina (ke kasaraa ke sath daal ( خدلا‏ . Mina ( riwayat kya hai lekin mana wahi hai."
5311,maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey shakhs ka hukm puchha jisne apni biwi par tohmat lagai ho to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Ajlan ke miyan biwi ke darmyan aisi sura mein judai kara di thi aur farmaya tha ke Allah khub janta hai ke tum mein se aik jhoota hai. to kya tum mein se aik (jo waqei gunah mein mubtala ho) rujoo karega lekin un donon ne inkar kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein judai kar di aur bayan kya ke mujh se Amr-bin-Dinar ne farmaya ke hadis ke kuchh ajzaa mera khayal hai ke maine abhi tum se bayan nahi kiye hain. farmaya ke un sahib ne (jinhon ne liaan kya tha) kaha ke mere maal ka kya hoga (jo maine mehar mein diya tha) bayan kya ke is par unse kaha gaya ke wo maal (jo aurat ko mehar mein diya tha) ab tumhara nahi raha. agar tum sachey ho (is tohmat lagaaney mein tab bhi kyonke) tum us aurat ke paas tanhai mein ja chukey ho aur agar tum jhootey ho tab to tum ko aur bhi mehar na milnaa chahiye .
5312,"unke mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tumhara hisab to Allah Taala ke zimme hai. tum mein se aik jhoota hai. ab tumhen tumhari biwi par koi ikhtiyar nahi. un sahabi ne arz kya ke mera maal wapas kara dijiye (jo mehar mein diya gaya thaa). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab wo tumhara maal nahi hai. agar tum iske maamle mein sachey ho to tumhara ye maal iske badle mein khatm ho chuka ke tum ne uski sharmgah ko halal kya tha aur agar tum ne is par jhooti tohmat lagai thi phir to wo tum se ba'eed tar hai. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke ye hadis maine Amr se yad ki aur Ayub ne bayan kya ke maine Saeed-bin-Jubair se suna, kaha ke maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey shakhs ke mutaalliq puchha jisne apni biwi se liaan kya ho to aap ne apni 2 ungliyon se ishara kya. Sufiyan ne us ishaare ko apni 2 shahadat aur beech ki ungliyon ko juda karke bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila bani Ajlan ke miyan biwi ke darmyan judai karaai thi aur farmaya tha ke Allah janta hai ke tum mein se aik jhoota hai, to kya wo rujoo kar lega? aap ne teen martaba ye farmaya, Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha ke Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne mujh se kaha, maine ye hadis jaisey Amr-bin-Dinar aur Ayub se sun kar yad rakhi thi waisii hi tujh se bayan kar di."
5313,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mard aur uski biwi ke darmyan judai kara di thi jinhoney apni biwi par tohmat lagai thi aur donon se qism li thi.
5314,qabila Ansar ke aik sahib aur unki biwi ke darmyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne liaan karaya tha aur donon ke darmyan judai kara di thi.
5315,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib aur unki biwi ke darmyan liaan karaya tha. phir un sahib ne apni biwi ke ladkey ka inkar kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ke darmyan judai kara di aur ladka aurat ko de diya.
5316,"liaan karne walon ka zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein hua to Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par aik baat kahi (ke agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi ko paon to wahin qatl kar daalun ( phir wapas aaey to unki qaum ke aik sahib unke paas aaey aur unse kaha ke maine apni biwi ke sath aik ghair mard ko paya hai. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke us maamle mein meri ye aazmaish meri is baat ki wjah se hui hai (jiske kehney ki jur'at maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ki thi) phir wo un sahib ko sath lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is sura se matla' kya jis mein unhon-ne apni biwi ko paya tha. ye sahib zard rang , kam gosht waley aur seedhey baalon waley they aur wo jisey unhon-ne apni biwi ke paas paya tha gehunwey rang , gathey jism ka zard , bharey gosht wala tha iske baal bahut zyada ghunghraaley they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allah ! mamla saaf kar de chunanche unki biwi ne jo bachcha janaa wo usi shakhs se mushabeh (similar) tha jiske mutaalliq shauhar ne kaha tha ke unhon-ne apni biwi ke paas usey paya tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ke darmyan liaan karaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aik shagird ne majlis mein poochha, kya ye wahi aurat hai jiske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar main kisi ko bila shahadat sangsaar karta to usey karta ? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi. ye dusri aurat thi jo Islam ke zamane mein ea'laaniya badkaarii kya karti thi."
5317,"Rifaa Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik khatun se nikah kya, phir unhein talaaq de di, iske baad aik doosrey sahib ne un khatun se nikah kar liya, phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur apne doosrey shauhar ka zikr kya aur kaha ke wo to unke paas aatey hi nahi aur ye ke unke paas kapdey ke pallu jaisa hai) unhon-ne pahley shauhar ke sath dobara nikah ki khahish zahir ki lekin) . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, jab tak tum us (doosrey shauhar (ka mazaa na chakh lo aur ye tumhara mazaa na chakh lein."
5318,"aik khatun jo Islam laai thin aur jinka naam sabeeaa tha, apne shauhar ke sath rehti thin, shauhar ka jab intiqal hua to wo haamla thin. abu-Sanaan bin ba'kak (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke paas nikah ka paigham bheja lekin unhon-ne nikah karne se inkar kya. abu-Sanaabil ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! jab tak iddat ki 2 muddaton mein se lambi na guzaar loongii , tumharey liye us se (jis se nikah wo karna chahti thiin) nikah karna sahi nahi hoga. phir wo ( waza' hamal ke baad) taqriban das din tak ruki rahen. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab nikah kar lo."
5319,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq kya fatwa diya tha to unhon-ne farmaya ke jab mere yahan bachcha paida ho gaya to Nabi Karim ne mujhey fatwa diya ke ab main nikah kar loon.
5320,sabeeaa Aslamiya apne shauhar ki wafat ke baad chand dinon tak haalate-nifaas mein rahiin. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar unhon-ne nikah ki ijazat mangi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat di aur unhon-ne nikah kya.
5321,"Yahyaa-bin-Saeed-bin-Aas ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Hakam ki sahibzadi (Umra) ko talaaq de di thi aur unke bap Abdur-Rehman unhein unke (shauhar ke) ghar se ley aaey (iddat ke din guzarney se pahley). Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko jab malum hua to unhon-ne Marwaan-bin-Hakam ke yahaan, jo us waqt Madina ka ameer tha, kahlwaayaa ke Allah se daro aur ladki ko uske ghar (jahaan usey talaaq hui hai) pahuncha do. jaisa ke Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ki hadis mein hai. Marwan ne usko jawab ye diya ke ladki ke walid Abdur-Rehman bin Hakam ne meri baat nahi maana aur Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke) Marwan ne Ummul-Momenin ko ye jawab diya ke) kya aapko Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke maamle ka ilm nahi hai? ( unhon-ne bhi apne shauhar ke ghar iddat nahi guzari thi). Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya ke agar tum Fatima ke waqia ka hawale na detey tab bhi tumhara kuchh na bigadtaa (kyonke wo tumharey liye daleel nahi bin saktaa) . Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne is par kaha ke agar aap ke nazdeek (Faatima (Raziallahu anhu) ka unke shauhar ke ghar se muntaqil karnaa) unke aur unke shauhar ke rishte daari ke darmyan kasheedgii ki wjah se tha to yahan bhi yahi wjah kafi hai ke donon ( miyan biwi (ke darmyan kasheedgii thi."
5322,"Yahya-bin-Saeed bin al-Aas ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Hakam ki sahibzadi (Umra) ko talaaq de di thi aur unke bap Abdur-Rehman unhein unke (shauhar ke) ghar se ley aaey (iddat ke din guzarney se pahley) . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko jab malum hua to unhon-ne Marwaan-bin-Hakam ke yahan , jo us waqt Madina ka ameer tha, kahlwaayaa ke Allah se daro aur ladki ko iske ghar ( jahan usey talaaq hui hai) pahuncha do. jaisa ke Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ki hadis mein hai. Marwan ne usko jawab ye diya ke ladki ke walid Abdur-Rehman bin-Hakam ne meri baat nahi maana aur Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke) Marwan ne Ummul-Momenin ko ye jawab diya ke) kya aapko Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke maamle ka ilm nahi hai? ( unhon-ne bhi apne shauhar ke ghar iddat nahi guzari thi). Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya ke agar tum Fatima ke waqia ka hawale na detey tab bhi tumhara kuchh na bigadtaa (kyonke wo tumharey liye daleel nahi bin saktaa). Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne is par kaha ke agar aap ke nazdeek (Faatima (Raziallahu anhu) ka unke shauhar ke ghar se muntaqil karna ( unke aur unke shauhar ke rishta daari ke darmyan kasheedgii ki wjah se tha to yahan bhi yahi wjah kafi hai ke donon ( miyan biwi (ke darmyan kasheedgii thi."
5323,"Fatima binte- Qais , Allah se dartii nahin! unka ishara unke us qaul ki taraf tha (ke baain talaaq wali ko) khaana-kharcha dena zaroori nahi jo kehti hai ke talaaq baain jis aurat par padey usey rehney aur kharcha nahi milega."
5324,"Fatima binte- Qais , Allah se dartii nahi ! unka ishara unke us qaul ki taraf tha (ke baain talaaq wali ko) khaana khacha dena zaroori nahi jo kehti hai ke talaaq baain jis aurat par padey usey maskan aur kharcha nahi milega."
5325,"aap fulaana ( Umra binte- hakam ( binte-Hakam ka mamla nahi dekhteen . unke shauhar ne unhein talaaqe-baain de di aur wo wahan se nikal aaein (iddat guzaarey baghair). Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke jo kuchh us ne kya bahut bura kya. Urwa ne kaha aap ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke waqia ke mutaalliq nahi suna. batlaya ke uske liye us hadis ko zikr karne mein koi khair nahi hai aur ibne-abi zanaad ne Hisham se ye izafa kya hai aur unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ( Umra binte-Hakam ke mamla par) apni shadeed na-gawari ka izhar farmaya aur farmaya ke Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) to aik ujaad jagah mein thin aur uske charon taraf khof aur wahshat barastii thi, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( wahan se muntaqil honey ki) unhein ijazat de di thi."
5326,"aap fulaana ( Umra binte-Hakam ( binte-Hakam ka mamla nahi dekhteen . unke shauhar ne unhein talaaq baain de di aur wo wahan se nikal aaein ( iddat guzaarey baghair ( . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke jo kuchh us ne kya bahut bura kya. Urwa ne kaha aap ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke waaqie ke mutaalliq nahi suna. batlaya ke uske liye is hadis ko zikr karne mein koi khair nahi hai aur ibne-abi zanaad ne Hisham se ye izafa kya hai aur unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne (Umra binte-Hakam ke maamle par) apni shadeed na-gawari ka izhar farmaya aur farmaya ke Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) to aik ujaad jagah mein thin aur uske charon taraf khof aur wahshat barastii thi, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( wahan se muntaqil honey ki) unhein ijazat de di thi."
5327,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki is baat ka (ke baain talaaq wali ko khaana-khacha nahi milega) inkar kya.
5328,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Fatima binte- Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki is baat ka (ke baain talaaq wali ko khaana kharcha nahi milega ( inkar kya.
5329,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa mein) kooch ka irada kya to dekha ke Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apne khema ke darwazey par ghamgeen khadi hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke) عقرى (ya ( farmaya rawi ko shak tha) ( حلقى ( malum hota hai ke tum hamein rok dogii, kya tum ne qurbani ke din tawaaf kar liya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir chalo."
5330,"Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni behan jameela ka nikah kya, phir (unke shauhar ne) unhein aik talaaq di."
5331,"Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan aik aadmi ke nikah mein thin, phir unhon-ne unhein talaaq de di, iske baad unhon-ne tanhai mein iddat guzari . iddat ke din jab khatm ho gaey to unke pahley shauhar ne hi phir Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unke liye nikah ka paigham bhejaa. Maaqil ko is par badi ghairat aai. unhon-ne kaha jab wo iddat guzaar rahi thi to usey is par qudrat thi (ke doran iddat mein rujoo kar lein lekin aisa nahi kya (aur ab mere paas nikah ka paigham bhejta hai. chunanche wo unke aur apni behan ke darmyan mein haail ho gaey. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( وإذا طلقتم Nisa فبلغن أجلهن فلا تعضلوهن‏ ( ''aur jab tum apni aurton ko talaaq de chuko aur wo apni muddat ko pahunch chukein to tum unhein mat roko.'' aakhir aayat tak phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bula kar ye aayat sunai to unhon-ne zid chhod di aur Allah ke hukm ke samney jhuk gaey."
5332,"unhon-ne apni biwi ko aik talaaq di to us waqt wo haaiza thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko hukm diya ke rujoo' kar lein aur unhein us waqt tak apne sath rakhein jab tak wo us haiz se paak honey ke baad phir dobara haaiza na hun. us waqt bhi unse koi baat-cheet na karein aur jab wo us haiz se bhi paak ho jayen to agar us waqt unhein talaaq dene ka irada ho to tuhur mein us se pahley ke unse ham-bistarii karein, talaaq dein. to yahi wo waqt hai jiske mutaalliq Allah Taala ne hukm diya hai ke usmein aurton ko talaaq di jaey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se agar iske (teen talaaq ke) barey mein sawal kya jata to sawal karne waley se wo kehtey ke agar tum ne teen talaaqein de di hain to phir tumhari biwi tum par haram hai. yahan tak ke wo tumharey siwa doosrey shauhar se nikah kare. (ghair Qutaiba) ke is hadis mein Leis se ye izafa kya hai ke (unhon-ne bayan kya ke) mujh se Naafe ne bayan kya aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tum ne apni biwi ko aik ya 2 talaaq de di ho. (to tum usey dobara apne nikah mein la saktey ho ( kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey iska hukm diya tha."
5333,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko talaaq de di, us waqt wo haaiza thin. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke ibne-Umar apni biwi se rujoo kar lein. phir jab talaaq ka sahi waqt aaey to talaaq dein ( Yunus bin Juber ne bayan kya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se) maine puchha ke kya is talaaq ka bhi shumaar hua tha? unhon-ne batlaya ke agar koi talaaq dene wala shara' ke ehkaam bajaa laney se aajiz ho ya ahmaq bewaqoof ho (to kya talaaq nahi padegii?) ."
5334,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas us waqt gaee jab unke walid Abu-Sufiyan bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) ka intiqal hua tha. Umme-Habiba ne khushbu mangwai jis mein khalooq khushbu ki zardi ya kisi aur cheez ki milawat thi, phir wo khushbu aik londi ne unko lagai aur Ummul-Momenin ne khud apne rukhsaaron par usey lagaya. iske baad kaha ke Allah ki qasam! mujhey khushbu ke istemal ki koi khahish nahi thi lekin maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho jaaiz nahi ke wo teen din se zyada kisi ka sog manaaey siwa shauhar ke (ke iska sog ( char mahiney das din ka hai."
5335,"iske baad mein Ummul-Momenin Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan us waqt gaee jab unke bhai ka intiqal hua. unhon-ne bhi khushbu mangwai aur istemal kya kaha ke Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ke istemal ki koi khahish nahi thi lekin maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par ye farmatey suna hai ke kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho ye jaaiz nahi ke kisi maiyat par teen din se zyada sog manaaey, sirf shauhar ke liye char mahiney das din ka sog hai."
5336,"aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri ladki ke shauhar ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur uski aankhon mein takleef hai to kya wo surma laga sakti hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke nahi, 2 teen martaba (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya (har martaba ye farmatey they ke nahi ! phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye ( sharaee iddat ( char mahiney aur das din hi ki hai. jahiliyat main to tumhen saal bhar tak mengni phenknii padtii thi (jab kahin iddat se bahar hoti thi)."
5337,iska kya matlab hai ke ''saal bhar tak mengni phenknii padtii thi? '' unhon-ne farmaya ke zamane jahiliyat mein jab kisi aurat ka shauhar mar jata to wo aik bahut hi zyada tang w taareek kothhrii mein dakhil ho jati. sabse burey kapdey pahantii aur khushbu ka istemal tark kar deti. yahan tak ke usi haalat mein aik saal guzar jata phir kisi chaupaaey gadhey ya bakri ya parinde ko uske paas laya jata aur wo iddat se bahar aaney ke liye is par hath phertii. aisa kam hota tha ke wo kisi janwar par hath pher de aur wo mar na jaey. iske baad wo nikaalii jati aur usey mengni di jati jisey wo phainktii. ab wo khushbu wghaira koi bhi cheez istemal kar sakti thi. Imam Malik se puchha gaya ke) تفتض به (ka kya matlab hai to aap ne farmaya wo uska jism chhootii thi.
5338,"aik aurat ke shauhar ka intiqal ho gaya, iske baad uski aankh mein takleef hui to iske ghar waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se surma lagaaney ki ijazat mangi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke surma ( zamana iddat mein) na lagaao .) zamana jahiliyat mein) tumhen badtareen kapdey mein waqt guzaarnaa padta tha, ya ( rawi ko shak tha ke ye farmaya ke) badtareen ghar mein waqt ( iddat ( guzaarnaa padta tha. jab is tarah aik saal pura ho jata to uske paas se kutta guzarta aur wo is par mengni phainktii (jab iddat se bahar aati ( to surma na lagaao . yahan tak ke char mahiney das din guzar jaaein."
5339,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik musalman aurat jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho. uske liye jaaiz nahi ke wo kisi (ki wafat (ka sog teen din se zyada manaaey siwa shauhar ke ke uske liye char mahiney das din hain.
5340,hamein mana kya gaya hai ke shauhar ke siwa kisi ka sog teen din se zyada manaaein .
5341,hamein us se mana kya gaya ke kisi maiyat ka teen din se zyada sog manaaein siwa shauhar ke ke uske liye char mahiney das din ki iddat thi. is arse mein ham na surma lagaatey na khushbu istemal kartey aur na ranga kapda pahntey they. albatta wo kapda us se alag tha jiska (dhaagaa) banney se pahley hi rang diya gaya ho. hamein uski ijazat thi ke agar koi haiz ke baad ghusl karey to us waqt azfaar ka thoda sa aud istemal kar ley aur hamein janaaze ke peechhey chalney ki bhi manaahii thi.
5342,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo aurat Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho uske liye jaaiz nahi ke teen din se zyada kisi ka sog manaaey siwa shauhar ke wo iske sog mein na surma lagaey na ranga hua kapda pahney magar Yaman ka dhaarii daar kapda (jo banney se pahley hi ranga gaya ho ( .
5343,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke) kisi maiyat par) khawind ke siwa teen din se zyada sog karne se aur) farmaya ke) khushbu ka istemal na karey, siwa tuhur ke waqt jab haiz se paak ho to thoda sa ud ( qist (aur ( maqam ( azfaar (ki khushbu istemal kar sakti hai) , abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke) qist (aur ( الكست ( aik hi cheez hain, jaisey '' kaafoor ''aur ''qaafoor'' donon aik hain."
5344,"aayate-karima ( والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا‏ ( الخ , yani ''aur jo log tum mein se wafat pa jayen aur beeviyan chhod jaaein. '' ke mutaalliq kaha ke ye iddat jo shauhar ke ghar walon ke paas guzari jati thi, pahley wajib thi, isliye Allah Taala ne ye aayat utaarii والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا وصية لأزواجهم متاعا إلى الحول غير إخراج فإن خرجن فلا جناح عليكم فيما فعلن في أنفسهن من معروف yaanii ''aur jo log tum mein se wafat pa jayen aur beeviyan chhod jayen (un par lazim hai ke) apni beeviyon ke haq mein nafa uthaney ki wasiiyat kar jayen ke wo aik saal tak ( ghar se) na nikaalii jayen lekin agar wo ( khud ( nikal jayen to koi gunah tum par nahiin '' is barey mein jisey wo ( beeviyan ( apne barey mein dastoor ke mutabiq karein. Mujahid ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne aisi bewa ke liye saat (7) mahiney bees din saal bhar mein se wasiiyat qarar di. agar wo chahey to shauhar ki wasiiyat ke mutabiq wahin thahrii rahe aur agar chahey (chaar mahiney das din ki iddat) poori karke wahan se chali jaey. Allah Taala ke irshad ( إخراج فإن خرجن فلا جناح عليكم‏ ( tak yani '' unhein nikala na jaey. albatta agar wo khud chali jayen to tum par koi gunah nahi. '' ka yahi mansha hai. to iddat to jaisi ke pahley thi, ab bhi is par wajib hai. ibne-abi najeeh ne usey Mujahid se bayan kya aur Ata ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke us pehli aayat ne bewa ko khawind ke ghar mein iddat guzarney ke hukm ko mansukh kar diya, isliye ab wo jahan chahey iddat guzaarey aur (isii tarah is aayat ne) Allah Taala ke irshad (ghair ikhraaj) yani '' unhein nikala na jaaey.'' (ko bhi mansukh kar diya hai). Ata ne kaha ke agar wo chahey to apne (shauhar ke) ghar walon ke yahan hi iddat guzaarey aur wasiiyat ke mutabiq qiyam karey aur agar chahey wahan se chali aaey kyonke Allah Taala ne farmaya hai) فلا جناح عليكم فيما فعلن‏ ( الخ , yani '' to tum par iska koi gunah nahi, jo wo apni marzii ke mutabiq karein. '' Ata ne kaha ke iske baad meeraas ka hukm nazil hua aur us ne makan ke hukm ko mansukh kar diya. to wo jahan chahey iddat guzaar sakti hai aur uske liye ( shauhar ki taraf se) makan ka intizam nahi hoga."
5345,jab unke walid ki wafat ki khabar pahunchi to unhon-ne khushbu mangwai aur apne donon baazuon par lagai phir kaha ke mujhey khushbu ki koi zarurat na thi lekin maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke jo aurat Allah aur aakhirat par eman rakhti ho wo kisi maiyat ka teen din se zyada sog na manaaey siwa shauhar ke ke uske liye char mahiney das din hain.
5346,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat, kaahin ki kamaaii aur zaaniya aurat ke zina ki kamaaii khaney se mana farmaya,"
5347,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne godney wali aur gudwaaney wali , sood khaney waley aur khilaaney waley par laanat bheji aur aap ne kuttey ki qeemat aur zaaniya ki kamaaii khaney se mana farmaya aur tasweer banaaney walon par laanat ki."
5348,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne laundiyon ke zina ki kamaaii se mana farmaya,"
5349,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey shakhs ke barey mein sawal kya jisne apni biwi par tohmat lagai ho to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila bani Ajlan ke miyan biwi mein judai kara di thi aur farmaya tha ke Allah khub janta hai ke tum mein se aik jhoota hai, to kya wo rujoo karega? lekin donon ne inkar kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai usey jo tum mein se aik jhoota hai wo tauba karta hai ya nahi ? lekin donon ne phir tauba se inkar kya. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein judai kara di. Ayub ne bayan kya ke mujh se Amr-bin-Dinar ne kaha ke haan, hadis mein aik cheez aur hai maine tumhen usey bayan kartey nahi dekha. wo ye hai ke) tohmat lagaaney waale) shauhar ne kaha tha ke mera maal ( mehar ( dilwaa dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke wo tumhara maal hi nahi raha, agar tum sachey bhi ho to tum us se khilwat kar chukey ho aur agar jhootey ho tab to tum ko kuchh milnaa hi nahi chahiye ."
5350,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne liaan karne waley miyan biwi se farmaya ke tumhara hisab Allah ke yahan hoga. tum mein se aik to yaqinan jhoota hai. tumharey yani ( shauhar ke) liye usey ( biwi ko) hasil karne ka ab koi rasta nahi hai. shauhar ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mera maal ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab wo tumhara maal nahi raha. agar tum ne iske mutaalliq sach kaha tha to wo iske badle mein hai ke tum ne uski sharmgah apne liye halal ki thi aur agar tum ne is par jhooti tohmat lagai thi tab to aur zyada tujh ko kuchh na milnaa chahiye .
